<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA525_01_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema525_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema525_01_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2 flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
        </h2>
        <div class="title_sub">
          <span lang="y">『수학 4-2』 수직</span>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">그림을 보고 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>&nbsp;안에 알맞은 기호를 써넣으세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="flex align_center dir_col gap_60">
          <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA525_01_IH/0002_img.png" alt="" /></div>
          <div class="question_box gap_8" lang="y">
            직선 가에 수직인 직선은 직선
            <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="다"></math-field></div>
            , 직선
            <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="라"></math-field></div>
            , 직선
            <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="바"></math-field></div>
            입니다.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">두 직선이 만나서 이루는 각이 직각일 때, 두 직선은 서로 수직입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve">
              <!--  -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
